data.description: Charming cul-de-sac home located in the desirable Dayton Valley Golf Community. Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a two car attached garage. Enjoy the spacious Great Room open to the Kitchen and a master suite featuring double sinks, a walk-in closet, shower stall and a private exit to the patio. Dayton Valley Golf Community is a gated neighborhood located in the heart of Dayton close to all the downtown Dayton amenities.
